{"id": 2929, "genre": 1000, "title": "对现在的你而言，人生绝对不能断了联系的人都有谁？", "description": "即便不怎么交流，但绝对不能完全失联的人都有谁？", "record_count": 15571, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190430115528hI0pN9PD8MWesRfx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5765, "title": "对现在的你而言，人生绝对不能断了联系的人都有谁？", "content": "对现在的你而言，人生绝对不能断了联系的人都有谁？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 341789, "content": "朝夕相处的宠物，哪怕出门也想用摄像头看看ta", "image": "img/option/option/20190430120444msul9f0EzD1U8otC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341793, "content": "童年最好的朋友，对方的联系方式绝对会保存着", "image": "img/option/option/20190430120845vmAGbhRqOlYs9DTu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341796, "content": "曾经的伴侣/配偶，即便分开也希望知道对方的消息", "image": "img/option/option/201904301215147LDHTViyo5BRxzCm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341834, "content": "喜欢/暗恋过的人，就算是单方面也想关注着", "image": "img/option/option/20190430133520aOznmdeC6pIFRL5x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341836, "content": "陪伴自己成长的家人，父母至亲", "image": "img/option/option/20190430133858ywkFS5zVvqe2BIX6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341838, "content": "一起工作“奋斗”的队友/搭档", "image": "img/option/option/20190430134227wM8yLYq0WJnTRdzg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341840, "content": "一起生活的对象，相爱的伴侣", "image": "img/option/option/20190430134700NT3ceob08tSFyZR7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341841, "content": "对自己有帮助的“良师益友”", "image": "img/option/option/201904301349207ILypBS2buma90X5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341788, "content": "有血缘关系的亲人，不论多生疏都有血缘纽带牵着", "image": "img/option/option/201904301203313KQUwmxILBcEit69.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 342577, "content": "没有不能失联的人，独自一个人也没问题", "image": "img/option/option/20190505075110rU2yCmWoRnV